subject: Breeders' Cup (Horse Races)
Horse Racing
lead_paragraph: Princess of Sylmar, a 3-year-old filly with humble beginnings, is a favorite to win the Breeders’ Cup Distaff on Friday and is a candidate for horse of the year.
